部有无核查，该工作人员答复称：“我们银行有，我们现在正在调查。” 1月21日下午，华商报大风新闻记者再次联系涉事银行，工作人员证实，此事发生在支行下面一个网点。 “这是几年前的事情了，不知道她近期因为什么，这个客户突然这两天又来到网点。具体情况我不太了解，因为我没有经办过这个事。” 记者询问是否未经客户本人同意办理业务，银行方面能否出示办理的凭证，该工作人员请示后答复称：“采访需要联系我们上级银行，这个涉及客户隐私，而且这个已经做过司法判决了，我们银行是没有责任的。”女子哭诉在银行定存80万被转成债券；涉事银行称无责任：正进行内部核查，双方均已报案_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"CkIIt52Bjv/78K1kEAMaCTExMzAxNjEyOSCuiL68BjAAON4GQA5yCzEwMjAwMzY4MjgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"43 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-79988043dbe8c35f47584afd141b6ab6_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1737627645.509990","card_id":"Q_10269024055","target":{"id":10269024055,"title":"柯洁 LG 杯提子违规被判负，在其他运动里相当于发生了什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/10269024055","type":"question","created":1737527621,"answer_count":338,"follower_count":478,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[744,1752,2955,164167,2487950],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkIIt52Bjv/78K1kEAMaCTExMzAyOTkxMyDFosK8BjAAON4DQA9yCzEwMjY5MDI0MDU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"35 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b5280b37182500a03859777ac97da265_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1737627645.510287","card_id":"Q_10158831005","target":{"id":10158831005,"title":"过年时，三十晚上都几点睡觉？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/10158831005","type":"question","created":1737425875,"answer_count":46,"follower_count":60,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3800233],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"比如:零点以后或看完春晚在睡等等？"},"attached_info":"CkEIt52Bjv/78K1kEAMaCTExMzAwNzc5NCDTh7y8BjAAODxAEHILMTAxNTg4